<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Signature non disponible — GestoPro</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f3f4f6; margin: 0; padding: 40px 16px; color: #111827; }
        .container { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.08); overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background: #1e293b; padding: 20px 28px; }
        .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; }
        .header h1 span { color: #60a5fa; }
        .body { padding: 36px 32px; text-align: center; }
        .icon { font-size: 44px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
        h2 { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 20px; color: #374151; }
        p { color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header"><h1>Gesto<span>Pro</span></h1></div>
    <div class="body">
        <div class="icon">⚠️</div>
        <h2>Signature non disponible</h2>
        <p>Ce devis ne peut pas être signé en ligne pour le moment (statut : <strong>{{ quote.status }}</strong>).</p>
        <p>Contactez {{ quote.user.fullName }} pour plus d'informations.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
